data.name: txtImdbWebUsername.ToolTip
data.value:
Your IMDb User ID starts with 'ur', you can get this from the IMDb website from the address bar when in your profile.
This option only works for profiles marked as 'Public'. Private profiles should use CSV option.

data.name: lblGenericFileImportDisclaimer.Text
data.value: The CSV file must contain an ImdbId column. That's the only column that will be used to import. Other columns will be ignored. If you have a flat file of only imdb ids, just make sure the first line is ImdbId and the following lines are the imdb ids, one on each line.
